---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import img1 from "../../images/services/img1.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<MainLayout title="Business Analysis">
  <div
    class="bg-detail-img bg-no-repeat h-96 w-full absolute top-0 grayscale -z-40"
  >
    <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-80 w-full h-full"></div>
  </div>
  <section class="mx-16 min-[1600px]:ml-32 flex text-white">
    <div class="mt-48 min-[1600px]:mt-72 gap-x-20">
      <header class="flex flex-col w-full items-center mb-72">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-semibold">Business Analysis</h2>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="h-full">
            <h2 class="text-5xl">
              We, at Digital & Design, help you make an informed decision by
              recording, tracking and analysing key data related to your
              business and help you move towards the right growth strategy.
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <Image src={img1} alt="img1" class="h-96 w-full object-fill" />
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-24 grid grid-cols-2 gap-16">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Data Analytics</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Most of the answers to growing your business lies in the data. Our
              service ensures the data is properly analysed to maximise ROI and
              increase the desirable results for your business to grow.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Research</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              The team at Digital & Design is fully equipped to carry out the
              sufficient Market Research to explain key factors of the industry
              and market to understand the consumer and what needs to be done to
              improve the business.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Marketing Performance</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Ensuring each Marketing decision performs at its optimal level, we
              have placed key indicators that are studied throughout a Marketing
              Campaignâ€™s duration to ensure the best results from all Marketing
              efforts for your brand.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Trends & Forecasting</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              TWe take data from your business, the industry and the market to
              develop trends that will allow our team to create an entire
              forecast for your business to set a benchmark upon.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
